Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SILVER-HAIRED HYM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so determined earlier,\Nbut you're still losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight back a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your Bloody Sukuraido!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that Air Strike attack of yours again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, you aren't just a pawn anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My Bloody Sukuraido! probably won't hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can no longer\Nbe killed by my Air Strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, most of my attacks\Nwon't have an effect on you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the rules of chess, a pawn\Nthat has gone deep into enemy territory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,can gain the abilities of a queen\Nor other powerful pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ascension of a pawn... A promotion!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That silver hair could be\Nproof of your promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof of your evolution\Nto a top-class warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you can't win,\Nyou'll just give up all fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those aren't the eyes\Nof someone who has given up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He still has something up his sleeve!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm beginning to see\Nthe weakness in Hym's movements!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right after throwing\Na destructive left punch,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym's entire body freezes\Nfor just an instant!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to attack\Nwith all my strength in that moment...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with my greatest, strongest attack!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your toys won't work anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Grand Cross!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally, it can be dodged,\Nbut if fired inward, there's no escape!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, it's time to experience hell with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He placed all his bets\Non that self-sacrificing attack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have worked\Nif it actually hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I beat you! I win, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my peak condition, I could have won.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've already used Grand Cross twice,\Nso focusing my Aura took too long.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I've used all my weapons\Nand all the energy I have.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm truly all out of options...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:06:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still kind of weird\Nhaving Popp heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I feel the same way.\NI only just attained the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you can cast heal-type spells,\Nyou didn't need to have Maam heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I really was\Nout of Magic Power at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp's so amazing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like\Nthere's less and less need for me...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're all fully healed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get us, Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of unsettling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't Master and Leona coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's been a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When entering an enemy's fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:07:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's actually a bad sign\Nfor enemies to suddenly not show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That usually means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. As you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it means someone powerful enough\Nto be entrusted with its defense is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It means there's no need\Nfor any weak guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the White Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Also known as the heart of Ban Palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which leads to the central tower,\Nthe Tower of Supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Past that is King Ban's chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most beautiful place\Nin Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, a sightseeing tour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd like to know\Nthe name of where you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not yet! I can't give up yet!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Leona told me\Nthat the power of my soul is Fortitude.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So long as there's even a shred\Nof fighting spirit left within me...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Hadorra, are you watching?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I've finally beaten\Na Disciple of Aban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he immortal?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he wants to fight until he dies.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, but I won't use my spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not just my spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aura against Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, I've cast away everything\Nin order to fight you on equal ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This fist will settle things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane, Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is made of Orichalcum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A human like you can't shatter me\Nwith your bare fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I can or not, I have to try first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This fist is the only weapon I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to wager\Neverything on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose, all that remains is death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you discard your armour and spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it to force myself into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first awoke to the Aura of Light,\NI tore steel apart with my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The flame of my life may grow weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I turn all of it into Aura\Nand focus it into my fist,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be strong enough\Nto penetrate your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll focus the last of my power\Ninto this fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more than\Njust a desperate measure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't bother, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your obsession for fighting\Nis impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're forgetting one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}GRAND CROSS{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My Heat Knuckle. No, it's a fist of Aura\Nso it's my Aura Knuckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no normal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Aura-infused Orichalcum,\Nso that's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how much\Nyou enhance your fist with Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My Aura Knuckle\Nis even harder than Orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you beat Dai or Lord Hadorra\Nempty-handed while they wield weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If this hits, it'll obliterate\Nnormal flesh beyond all recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die\Nin such a pitiful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating you was the first\Npurpose in life I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment I saw you, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk around like\Nyou're the strongest there ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning that cool expression\Ninto one of fear was my one dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed that doing so\Nwould serve Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're going to die,\Ndon't die in a pathetic way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to die as you lived.\NWith a cool look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, when we first fought,\Nyou said something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's better to die beautifully\Nthan to live in disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true I don't fear death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a time when I preferred\Na glorious death to a life of disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But not anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends showed me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A true warrior cannot ever give up\Nuntil they fulfill their purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means eating mud,\None must carry out their duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how disgraceful\Nor pathetic it may seem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's even a sliver of a chance,\NI'm going to bet on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come on, Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This fist carries all of my fortitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it beat your implacable fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are an amazing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally realize what it is about you\Nthat I wanted to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an amazing individual, too, Hym.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're second person\Nto ever drive me this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch me, my friend!\NThis is my last great gambit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym backed off.\NHere comes Hym's greatest attack!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow everything away\Nwith my burning fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aura Knuckle!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad, Hym.\NYour fist never touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My desperate strike\Nhit you before you could!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fist that won!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won. It took everything I had\Nto pull it off.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym truly was a powerful foe.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. How could my Orichalcum body...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because your attack\Nwas just that powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My Aura and strength aren't enough\Nto shatter Orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized I had to use the force\Nof your charge and counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Aban Style has a similar skill.\NI just applied it to my fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you used when fighting Baran...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the Hollow Stance requires emptying\Noneself and taking an enemy blow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had tried that here, even with my\NAura suppressed, one blow would kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I had no choice but to hit you\Nwith my Aura-infused fist first.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The timing was truly\Na life-or-death instant.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I managed to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because you accepted\Na head-on challenge from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you could have used\Nyour martial arts to whittle me down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and gained a sure victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even knowing that would bring me victory,\NI'd never do that. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Beating you like that would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give my life to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd rather die than win like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting wounded used to only\Ncause me a tiny bit of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is the pain of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've won.\NNow finish me like a victor should!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't someone who should die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you reach my friends,\Nthey can heal you with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up and go to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it my all and lost!\NI have no regrets! I don't need your pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,An order?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If the victor has the right\Nto take the life of the defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then I take your death, not your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't evil anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wish to defeat me was a pure one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no need\Nto finish you off in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nyour life is no longer just your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry the lives of Hadorra\Nand the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you gained a new life\Njust because of a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an obligation\Nto live on for your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Hym?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I survive the upcoming battle,\Nthen I'll gladly fight you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So live on, Hym. With us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't come out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When my friends said it to me,\Nit came out kinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you and your arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could move,\NI'd punch you in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it after you survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this shaking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the Cleaner of Ban Palace\Nhas finally lost patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cleaner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there seven pawns just like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's Sigma and Block and Fenbren!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about,\Nyou useless piece of scrap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?\NChess involves a king and a queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,two bishops, two rooks, two knights,\Nand eight pawns, making 16 pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban only gave Hadorra five of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And of the 16 pieces,\Nonly one has its own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The one King Ban truly trusts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban Palace's greatest\Nand most powerful guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The king, Maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good! Hyunckel's in tatters\Nand I can't move!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't stand a chance\Nagainst that many Orichalcum warriors!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run Hyunckel! Just leave me and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me. I don't think\NI can keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still have to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? You have to get to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You're not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've fought.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fought all this way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believed that only my pain\Ncould make me forget my past.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That only the blood and sweat I spill\Ncould wash away my sins.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all ends today!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:22:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no doubt.\NThis will be my last battle!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:17.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:28.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:36.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:45.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:49.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:56.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:02.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:09.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:15.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:20.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:27.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel proved victorious over Hym.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as a bond is formed between the two,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Maximum appears\Nleading an Orichalcum Army.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The chess army and Maximum\Nattack the wounded Hyunckel mercilessly.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Hyunckel and Hym overcome\Nthis perilous situation?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Checkmate"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
